1. Install vpp.

Download these rpms:
vpp-18.07-1.x86_64.rpm
vpp-lib-18.07-1.x86_64.rpm
vpp-selinux-policy-18.07-1.x86_64.rpm
from 
http://mirror.centos.org/centos/7/nfv/x86_64/fdio/vpp/vpp-1807/



2. Setup env.

Download kvm from
https://download.clearlinux.org/image/clear-26850-kvm.img.xz
and fd file
https://download.clearlinux.org/image/OVMF.fd

guest host 1 <—> VPP(Bridge) <—> guest host 2


More details:
https://blog.csdn.net/u010827484/article/details/80685841


